\c 70 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 70\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waammata Birmataa (Far.\bd 40\bd*:\bd 13\bd*-\bd 17\bd*)(Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; kan Daawit; isa yeroo ixaanni aarfamutti faarfatamu)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, dafii na oolchi, yaa Waaqayyo, na gargaaruudhaaf ariifadhu!
\m \bd 2\bd* Warri jireenya koo balleessuu barbaadan, haa yeella'an, haa qaana'anis! Warri hamaan ana argachuutti gammadan, gara booddee deebi'anii haa salphifaman.
\m \bd 3\bd* Warri "Baga, baga" anaan jedhan, qaana'anii gara booddeetti haa deebi'an!
\m \bd 4\bd* Warri si barbaadan hundinuu garuu, isaanitti haa tolu, sittis haa gammadan! Warri fayyisuu kee jaallatanis utuu gargar hin kutin, "Waaqayyo guddaa dha!" haa jedhan.
\m \bd 5\bd* Waa'ee koof yoo ta'e garuu, ani gadadamaa dha, dhabaa dhas, ariifadhuu na bira ga'i, yaa Waaqayyo! ati gargaarsa koo ti, furii koo tis, yaa Waaqayyo, egaa hin turin!
\b 
